A woman wrote a book about the senses and a guy went blind.

25:43.855 --> 25:44.637
He loved his book.

25:45.022 --> 25:46.224
Story about that in the Times today.

25:46.244 --> 25:46.865
It was an article.

25:47.105 --> 25:47.606
Okay.

